test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 10000 == 10
 +  where 10000 = <built-in function prod>([10, 1, 2, 5, 10, 1, ...])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x74468a129a40>([10])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x74468a129a40> = [[10, 1, 10, 1, 10, 1], [10, 1, 10, 1, 10, 1], [10, 1, 10, 1, 10, 1]].count
